            <title><![CDATA[Trails in the Sky 1st Chapter version 1.05 update now available, adds first-person mode]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/10/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-version-1-05-update-now-available-adds-first-person-mode</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-version-1-05-update-now-available-adds-first-person-mode.1321537/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Plus the option to hide the user interface.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > Nihon Falcom [758 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/nihon-falcom">Falcom</a> has <a href="https://twitter.com/nihonfalcom/status/1976481932897857966" target="_blank">released</a> the version 1.05 update for <em><a title="Games > Trails in the Sky 1st Chapter [25 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter">Trails in the Sky 1st Chapter</a></em> on <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,590 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a> and <a title="Platforms > PC [24,501 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a>, which adds a first-person view mode and an option to hide the user interface, among other updates. The <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [546 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a> and Switch versions will follow at a later date. <span id="more-999141"></span></p><p>Here are the patch notes:</p><blockquote><ul><li>Added “Image Quality / Performance Settings” to the <em><a title="Platforms > Switch [17,816 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Nintendo Switch</a> 2 Edition</em>.</li><li>Added options to adjust text speed and text auto-advance speed.</li><li>Added one-key shortcuts for <a title="Genres > Action [3,121 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/action">action</a>s that normally require two key presses on keyboard.</li><li>Added a first-person mode.</li><li>Added the option to hide in-game user interface.</li></ul><table><thead><!-- AD: content -->
        <tr><th></th><th>First-Person Mode</th><th>Hide User Interface</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><th>Switch 2 / Switch</th><td>R + ZL</td><td>R + ZR</td></tr><tr><th>PlayStation 5</th><td>R1 + L2</td><td>R1 + R2</td></tr><tr><th>Steam Gamepad</th><td>RB + LT</td><td>RB + RT</td></tr><tr><th>Steam Keyboard</th><td>Insert</td><td>X</td></tr></tbody></table><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Trails-in-the-Sky-1st-Chapter-Update_10-09-25_001.jpg"></a></figure><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Trails-in-the-Sky-1st-Chapter-Update_10-09-25_002.jpg"></a></figure><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Trails-in-the-Sky-1st-Chapter-Update_10-09-25_003.jpg"></a></figure><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Trails-in-the-Sky-1st-Chapter-Update_10-09-25_004.jpg"></a></figure><ul><li>Corrected various text errors.</li><li>Fixed other miscellaneous bugs.</li></ul></blockquote><p><em>Trails in the Sky 1st Chapter</em> is available now for PlayStation 5, Switch 2, Switch, and PC via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3375780/Trails_in_the_Sky_1st_Chapter/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>.</p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/10/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-version-1-05-update-now-available-adds-first-person-mode]]></content:encoded>
